<p>You can use the deployment scenarios to familiarize yourself with HPE Helion OpenStack(R) Carrier Grade and evaluate its performance.</p>
<!-- ===================== horizontal rule ===================== -->
<p>
<b>Note:</b> This feature applies only to servers in the VNF Region.</p>
<!-- ===================== horizontal rule ===================== -->
<p>Two deployment scenarios are described:</p>
<ul>
<li>
<b>Bridging Scenario</b> -This scenario uses two virtual L2 switches</li>
<li>
<b>Routing Scenario</b> - This scenario uses two virtual L3 switches. </li>
</ul>
<p>In each scenario, two VM instances are launched, and a test path is established between them for performance evaluations.</p>
